verbose_text: 11 In osteoarthritic chondrocyte culture the IL-1beta induced synthesis of matrix metalloproteinase 13 (MMP-13) is inhibited by the preincubation with HMWHA, 35 on the contrary the presence of HA oligosaccharides induces in chondrocyte culture MMP-13 synthesis.
